{"tid":719348,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【公司市值26億】107億賣北美業務 利標特別息高過股價！","createTime":"2018-06-27T10:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T14:47:17.000Z","uid":174649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"661d08a2371ca1b731b025efda95d8ff4b4bf5af","tid":719348,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180627/large/1530093990_84dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180627%2Flarge%2F1530093990_84dd.jpg&h=f79993b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利標（787）公布出售北美業務，代價13.8億美元（折合港元約107.64億），並擬最多派特別息0.325元。利標股價今日跌6.2%，報0.305元，即特別息高於股價。公司最新市值為26億元。<br />\n<br />\n利標稱公司已同意出售其大部份北美特許授權業務，包括童裝、配飾及時裝業務，予納斯達克上市公司Differential Brands Group Inc，應付現金購買價為13.8億美元，可予調整，待股東會批准作實。所得資金將用以償還債務、派息及營運。<br />\n相關業務截至今年3月31日止年度，銷售額約22億美元，佔利標收入約55%。<br />\n據利標2018財政年度中期業績報告，公司計息負債多達200億元。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4a2ac8d7e1350e8089007a8da5132805204b54","tid":719348,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"聽日開市0.6"},{"pid":"fd17cb1e8127217f8d69c02b8cd762ec4f7e8c34","tid":719348,"uid":59690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b4a2ac8d7e1350e8089007a8da5132805204b54","tid":719348,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"聽日開市0.6"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"唔奇"},{"pid":"82b7dc032fce5c4ae05e3960a464c737ec0ffb22","tid":719348,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"開市$1"},{"pid":"7cfbd4b888aeb322a655ca9ed9b22538b8264d67","tid":719348,"uid":42395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"除淨日高唔過 0.6 到時點計"},{"pid":"9e3801da85662abd3c20f24b92f793680d001ee4","tid":719348,"uid":71748,"like